text.tspan: Cumulative CO₂ emissions by world region
Cumulative carbon dioxide (CO₂) emissions by region from the year 1750 onwards. Emissions are based on territorial emissions
(production-based) and do not account for emissions embedded in trade. This measures CO₂ emissions from fossil fuels and
cement production only – land use change is not included.
Source: Our World in Data based on the Global Carbon Project
